latestIgtvVideos.caption:
@barbieferreira for @voguemagazine’s 7 days, 7 looks is live on YouTube!

i created barbie’s everyday glam variations using these #yslbeauty products:

-nu barelook tint 3 on interior of face
-nu barelook tint 5 on exterior of face for dimension
-satin crush mono eyeshadow in extreme copper on her eyelid blended up
-curled lash and applied several coats of lash clash
-nu glow balm applied to the high planes of the face and eyelid 
-for lips we alternated between (my fave) rouge volupté candy glaze in sweet pink, slim matte rouge in paradoxe, water stain lip in submerged coral and the later two layered 

best time best crew! @chrishoran20 @saintasylum @tejbee @yslbeauty special thanks to @becomingeden
